desc.en: It was created by METRO Xiaogangguan, an author from bilibli, and METRO Xiaogangguan, an author from Kuaishou. By drawing on the names of some stations of Guangzhou Metro and creating their own station names, the rail transit system of Puyang City was developed. The current version is v0.6, and it was produced at 16:49 on May 17, 2025. It can be referred to.
